@abstract:
Declared intent and purpose for Echidna.
@end

## Purpose

Echidna is a trust-hardened neurosymbolic theorem proving platform.
It supports 48 prover backends, records every proof attempt to VeriSimDB,
and feeds the Hypatia learning loop so the fleet gets smarter over time.

## Anti-Purpose

This project is NOT:
- A fork or wrapper around another tool
- A monorepo (unless explicitly structured as one)

## If In Doubt

If you are unsure whether a change is in scope, ask.
Sensitive areas: ABI definitions, license headers, CI workflows.
